*colorsvn-0.3.2-r2 (16 Sep 2010)

  16 Sep 2010; Christian Ruppert <idl0r@gentoo.org> +colorsvn-0.3.2-r2.ebuild,
  +files/0001-Don-t-colorize-svn-mkdir-bug-321451.-Use-IPC-open2-i.patch:
  Don't use stderr anymore, bug 326279. Move sed to add 'svn mkdir' to the
  preventcolor array into the patch as well. Use make -j1 for now, bug 335134.

